    "# Problem 23: The AGV Dispatching & Battery Management Problem\n",
    "\n",
    "## Tier 7: The Human-AI Symbiotic Partnership (The Centaur Model)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Goal\n",
    "Implement a Human-AI symbiotic partnership where human operators collaborate with autonomous AI systems, combining human intuition and strategic reasoning with AI computational power and pattern recognition.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Assumptions\n",
    "- Human operators provide high-level goals and handle exceptions\n",
    "- AI systems manage routine operations and provide recommendations\n",
    "- Explainable AI (XAI) makes AI decisions transparent and understandable\n",
    "- Human operators can override AI decisions when necessary\n",
    "- The system learns from human feedback and improves over time\n",
    "\n",
    "### Approach (Step-by-Step)\n",
    "1. **Control Tower Design**: Create human-AI collaboration interface\n",
    "2. **Goal-Oriented Control**: Human operators set high-level objectives\n",
    "3. **Explainable AI**: AI explains its reasoning and decisions\n",
    "4. **Anomaly Detection**: AI alerts humans to unusual patterns\n",
    "5. **Strategic Override**: Humans can intervene in critical situations\n",
    "6. **Learning Loop**: System learns from human decisions and feedback\n",
    "7. **Performance Analytics**: Measure human-AI collaboration effectiveness\n",
    "\n",
    "### What to Look for in the Results\n",
    "- Improved decision quality through human-AI collaboration\n",
    "- Explainable AI reasoning that humans can understand\n",
    "- Effective anomaly detection and human intervention points\n",
    "- Learning and improvement from human feedback\n",
    "- Balanced workload between human operators and AI systems\n",
    "\n",
    "### Concrete Example\n",
    "We'll implement a Human-AI symbiotic system with 2 human operators managing 8 AGVs, demonstrating goal-oriented control, explainable AI, strategic override, and collaborative decision-making."
   ]
